data.enText: having the same size and shape

data.chText: 适合的；适当的；恰当的；相称的
data.enText: suitable for sth; appropriate in a particular situation

value.def: If one thing is congruent with another thing, they are similar or fit together well.

example.ex: They want to work in an organisation whose values are congruent with their own.
example.tran: 他们想在一个符合自己价值观的机构里工作。
